Siaya Governor Cornel Rasanga has told Nicholas Gumbo to stop causing confusion by using ODM colours.Gumbo will run for governor as an independent.Rasanga said the law is clear on symbols and colours of political parties and the independents.He spoke on Thursday, shortly after he was given a go ahead by the IEBC.Gumbo accused Rasanga of using relief food to lure voters, saying it is against the law to campaign using state machinery.